  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A varied continental buffet is served each morning with hot options served to order. Expect fresh fruit, yogurts, breads, cakes and freshly-brewed Italian coffee.</p>
<p><strong>The Terrace</strong> is open from 12.30pm to 5pm and 7pm to 10pm. It's got a varied Mediterranean menu that uses the freshest ingredients possible including fish from the lake and local wines to complement each meal. Click here to view the current <a href="https://www.belvederebellagio.com/media/82826/2019_IlPranzoHB.pdf">lunch</a> and <a href="https://www.belvederebellagio.com/media/82829/2019_LaCenaHB.pdf">dinner</a> menus. If you choose half board, you'll eat dinner here from a set menu.</p>
<p><strong>The Veranda</strong> offers seasonal cuisine and fine wines to match the menu. Floor-to-ceiling windows let light flood in and you can even enjoy views of the lake with your meal.</p>
<p><strong>The Lounge Bar</strong> is a good spot to relax with an afternoon tea with home-made pastries or savour a late-night digestive.</p>
<p>Early meals for children are available on request. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
