  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Belvedere is one of <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como's</a> best hotels. It's got fantastic lake views from it's location just above Bellagio. Head for the pool or gardens to enjoy them or upgrade to a lake view room and you'll get to wake up to them every day. The staff are very welcoming here and the whole place feels really comfortable and luxurious.</p>]]></listingDescription>
