  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are finished in a modern style with traditional touches like parquet floors and Italian-made furniture. These rooms sleep up to three people and measure around 22m². They have a double or twin beds, air conditioning, TV, free Wi-Fi, safe, minibar, hairdryer and a bathtub or shower.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> can sleep up to two people and have views over Lake Como. They offer more space at 25m² and some rooms have a whirlpool bathtub.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are around 36m² and have a lounge area with comfy sofas. Lake views can be enjoyed from the private balcony. These rooms can sleep up to two people and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Rooms for sole use are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
